Description: A modular, modern simulation suite and toolkit for simulating transmission networks,
    phylogenies, and evolutionary pairwise distance matrices under different models and assumptions
    for viral/sequence evolution. While intially developed for HIV, SEEPS offers modular
    utilities for custom workflows for extension beyond HIV.
